function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
$cont = @file_get_contents('changelog.json.php');
if ($cont === false) err('Cannot read changelog.json.php');
$json = @json_decode($cont, true);
if ($json === null) err('Cannot parse changelog.json.php');
$latest_version = false;
foreach ($json as $v) {
	if (isset($v['version']) && (substr($v['version'], -4) != '-dev')) {
		$latest_version = $v['version'];
		break; // the first item is the latest version
	}
}
if ($latest_version != '2.0.2.4') err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.2.4!');

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.4.0') < 0) {
	err('You need at least PHP Version 7.4 to update to this version');
}

@mkdir('userdata_pub/plugins');
if (!is_dir('userdata_pub/plugins')) {
	warn('Directory could not be created: userdata_pub/plugins');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('userdata_pub/plugins', 0755)) {
	warn('Could not change directory permissions of userdata_pub/plugins');
}

// File added: userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt
function writefile_11() {
	$fp = @fopen('userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt', 'w');
	if ($fp === false) {
		warn('File userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt cannot be written');
		return;
	}
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('CkFib3V0IHRoZSBmb2xkZXIgInVzZXJkYXRhX3B1Yi9wbHVnaW5zIgotLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0KCkFzIGFsdGVybmF0aXZlIHRvIHRoZSBwbHVnaW5zLyBmb2xkZXIsCnlvdSBjYW4gcGxhY2UgcGx1Z2lucyBpbgoidXNl'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('cmRhdGFfcHViL3BsdWdpbnMiIG9yCiJ1c2VyZGF0YV9wdWIvdGVuYW50Ly4uLi9wbHVnaW5zIi4K'));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (is_file('userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt') && (sha1_file('userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt') != '23a77d251ecfb70d2e2e709291be7ac62f0d4399')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt');
	$tmp = pathinfo('userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_11();
if (!is_file('userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt');
} else if (sha1_file('userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt') != '23a77d251ecfb70d2e2e709291be7ac62f0d4399') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of userdata_pub/plugins/info.txt');
}

if (!is_file('TODO')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: TODO');
	writefile_12();
	if (!is_file('TODO')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): TODO');
	} else if (sha1_file('TODO') != 'a79ac6e883f785b680fa728900df1f9ecc6b2e81') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): TODO');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('TODO', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of TODO');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'a79ac6e883f785b680fa728900df1f9ecc6b2e81') {
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '30fd30e4d7dfc4c997900ca78e014158542c93b4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: TODO');
			$tmp = pathinfo('TODO');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('TODO')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('TODO', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_12();
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'a79ac6e883f785b680fa728900df1f9ecc6b2e81') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): TODO');
		}
	}
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('TlR8SlNPTl9VTkVTQ0FQRURfU0xBU0hFUyk7Cgl9CgoJQGhlYWRlcignQ29udGVudC1UeXBlOmFwcGxpY2F0aW9uL2pzb247IGNoYXJzZXQ9dXRmLTgnKTsKCgllY2hvICRvdXQ7Cn0K'));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: ajax.php');
	writefile_13();
	if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): ajax.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('ajax.php') != '224e333adcb0e20039af227c02f94bea627ff17c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('ajax.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of ajax.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '224e333adcb0e20039af227c02f94bea627ff17c') {
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '2a9814a6b2b1ecc73f538d1b177a176c89d70868') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: ajax.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('ajax.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('ajax.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('ajax.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_13();
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '224e333adcb0e20039af227c02f94bea627ff17c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: changelog.json.php');
	writefile_14();
	if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): changelog.json.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('changelog.json.php') != '94eba83f602717654d7375482ae229d3c219cb9e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('changelog.json.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of changelog.json.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '94eba83f602717654d7375482ae229d3c219cb9e') {
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '0d7b114ba14c8c7d673870790e5819495b5a304a') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: changelog.json.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('changelog.json.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('changelog.json.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('changelog.json.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_14();
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '94eba83f602717654d7375482ae229d3c219cb9e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
		}
	}
}

	} else if (sha1_file('dev/release.sh') != '24a5a3e9cb344b444906a7ad6d9f63e72607fc69') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/release.sh');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/release.sh', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/release.sh');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/release.sh') !== '24a5a3e9cb344b444906a7ad6d9f63e72607fc69') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/release.sh') !== '3da8c8a329a10d75a140d4e27302f89925f1c749') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/release.sh');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/release.sh');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/release.sh')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/release.sh', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_15();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/release.sh') !== '24a5a3e9cb344b444906a7ad6d9f63e72607fc69') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/release.sh');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	writefile_16();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') != 'eda163a8b8e7695419f06acf53a52b95edc404fb') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== 'eda163a8b8e7695419f06acf53a52b95edc404fb') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '0902c77d63ffb51eefe5b5febda7090d2c5becf4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_16();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== 'eda163a8b8e7695419f06acf53a52b95edc404fb') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php') != '4bae4608d7e1c56c92d060af05718a69b7c1d56a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php', 0644)) {

	}

	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php') !== '4bae4608d7e1c56c92d060af05718a69b7c1d56a') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php') !== 'be5be06dc650712005567c9b445ca9297174d632') {

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php') !== '4bae4608d7e1c56c92d060af05718a69b7c1d56a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php');

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php');
	writefile_23();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php') != 'cf1c8b8bd0e07d64149d6b779e57afd732bc006f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php') !== 'cf1c8b8bd0e07d64149d6b779e57afd732bc006f') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php') !== '3b4c3082a7e32494725b423f835955bc5a7668b1') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_23();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php') !== 'cf1c8b8bd0e07d64149d6b779e57afd732bc006f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/401_backup/restore_backup.php');
		}
	}
}

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php') !== '87fcd54bf3440b8af872ca219760b3050f671cec') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_34();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php') !== 'cad8ce9405aee0093e23ca0e407e07015dad04d4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') != '35bcfd8c21a8659d5c3cdd829811815a772b6f33') {

	}

				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') !== '35bcfd8c21a8659d5c3cdd829811815a772b6f33') {
